item.title: Error connecting to server
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

The reason you can’t connect is because you MUST use 127.0.0.1 if you are connecting and running on the same machine.

The reason you have to change your IP when uploading it to a site is because, well, then you’re not running it on the same machine.
